
  Volbeat    Bug Type Pokémon

  With the arrival of night, VOLBEAT 
  emits light from its tail.  It 
  communicates with others by adjusting 
  the intensity and flashing of 
  its light.  Volbeat is attracted 
  by the sweet aroma of ILLUMISE. 
  
  Single Stage Evolution Pokémon

